@model Deals
@section stylesCategory{ @*bunu ona gore yazdiqki burda yazilan css shared papkasinda loayout.cshtml icerisinde render ede bilek*@
<style>
    label {
        color: red;
    }
</style>
}
<form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
    @*<div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly" style="color:red"></div>*@
    <div class="mb-3">
        <label>Image</label>
        <input type="file" class="form-control" asp-for="Photo">
        <span asp-validation-for="Photo" style="color:red"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-3">
        <label>Name</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" asp-for="Name">
        <span asp-validation-for="Name" style="color:red"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-3">
        <label>Title</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" asp-for="Title">
        <span asp-validation-for="Title" style="color:red"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-3">
        <label>PresentPrice</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" asp-for="PresentPrice">
        <span asp-validation-for="PresentPrice" style="color:red"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-3">
        <label>PastPrice</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" asp-for="PastPrice">
        <span asp-validation-for="PastPrice" style="color:red"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-3">
        <label>Date</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" asp-for="Date">
        <span asp-validation-for="Date" style="color:red"></span>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
</form>